n8n - GeeksforGeeks
hits.snippet: n8n an open-source workflow automation platform, enables users to visually create workflows with a node-based interface. Unlike typical no-code tools, it supports developers with JavaScript, API calls and self-hosting. With over 200 integrations like Google Sheets, Slack, GitHub, etc. It offers cloud-based and self-hosted options, providing businesses flexibility in workflow management.
